<li class="product-card |attr available ? 'is-available' : 'is-sold-out'|">
   <strong>|name|</strong>
   <span>₱|price|</span>
   |if available|
      <span>Available</span>
   |else|
      <span>Sold out</span>
   |/if|

   |if tags|
      <small>Has tags</small>
   |else|
      <small>No tags</small>
   |/if|
</li>